reviewText: Howdy;As with the "Great Smoky Mountains" this is another in a great series for national park videos.The narration and music are great and the interviews are most interesting.Running time is 80 minutes.Hope this helps out, L8R daze...
Title: National Parks Exploration Series: The Everglades - A Subtropical Paradise

reviewText: It is a very well done video of the park.  It is divided into three parts .  Each section is chuck full of information.  The scenery filmed was great a great piece of work.  I lived Florida for 17 years.  I have been there. It's a great buy!
summary: National Parks Exploration Series: The Everglades - A Subtropical Paradise [Blu-ray] (2012)
Title: National Parks Exploration Series: The Everglades - A Subtropical Paradise

reviewText: The Everglades National Park HD Blu-ray video is a quality presentation and is most enjoyable. The photography is beautiful and the naritive information proivided on the history of the park is very well done. I highly recommend it to those that have an interest in the National Parks and their history.
summary: Nat Parks: The Everglades - A Subtropical Paridise
Title: National Parks Exploration Series: The Everglades - A Subtropical Paradise

reviewText: I liked the experienced guide that took his group on tour. I would have enjoyed watching more side films of what he was teaching the group while out in the park instead of viewing him speaking to the group as much as was filmed. It was beautiful on blue ray when scenery and wildlife was shown.
Title: National Parks Exploration Series: The Everglades - A Subtropical Paradise
